{
  "stem": "23428.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was just saying that I was summoned for that offense.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was a sort of offense for which I knew, exactly, people paid with their lives in the camp.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But somehow, I attributed it again, like at the time of my interrogation in Budapest, to my military manners, my perfect German.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This guy was Ukrainian because they were-- the SS were mostly non-German speaking Ukrainians and Yugoslavs in the camps.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Obviously, people couldn't be trusted to fight.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So-- so they employed them in these jobs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Well, anyway, this guy must have been impressed by my youth, by my innocent looks, by my Prussian manners, whatnot.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So after ripping off a few of-- my-- my number, and a few of the buttons that were in the wrong place, I was given the sign to-- to leave.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was-- ran off happy to have my life saved.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] OK.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It must have been after this incidence that I developed a viral disease-- red pimples that spread over the entire leg.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And people were hysterical about infectious diseases in the camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I was placed instantly into the hospital block, [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] where I was not allowed to get out.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and my brother, in the evening, after coming back from the work detail-- he always came to the-- the window in the block to find me.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Well, that-- one day he didn't anymore.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And apparently what had happened is they had taken him to Sachsenhausen, which was the concentration camp closest to Berlin.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I know this only from later from documentation because he was registered there as a Hungarian interpreter.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the same thing once more in Buchenwald, when he perished.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
